		"Harry Potter and the Philosopher's/Sorcerer's Stone
	]em
	" as Harry attends his first year at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. Despite the large number of adaptations out there, at the start of 2015 this is only the first Harry Potter game to receive a movie on TASVideos.
